  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 230&deg;C/ 210&deg;C (fan)/ 450&deg;F/ Gas 8</p>\r\n<p>Lay the strips of <strong>streaky bacon</strong> onto a baking tray (use foil to avoid mess!)</p>\r\n<p>Put the tray in the oven for 10-15 min or until slightly crispy</p>\r\n<p>Once done, transfer the <strong>cooked bacon</strong> to a chopping board to cool and keep the baking tray for later</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a matching lid with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced chicken</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Cover and cook for 3-4 min or until nicely browned and cooked through then remove from the heat and keep covered until later</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the<strong> capers</strong> coarsely</p>\r\n<p>Strip the <strong>tarragon leaves</strong>&nbsp;from their stalks and chop the<strong>&nbsp;leaves</strong>&nbsp;finely&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut<strong>&nbsp;</strong>the <strong>ciabatta<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into bite-size cubes</p>\r\n<p>Add the<strong> ciabatta cubes</strong> to the bacon tray, drizzle them with <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the tray in the oven for 4-8 min or until the ciabatta is crunchy and just&nbsp;beginning to brown - these are your <strong>croutons&nbsp;</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>chopped capers</strong>,<strong>&nbsp;tarragon</strong>, <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>mayonnaise</strong>, <strong>Dijon mustard</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> to a large salad bowl</p>\r\n<p>Season&nbsp;with <strong>pepper</strong> and mix well - this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p>\r\n<p>Chop the <strong>cooled</strong> <strong>bacon</strong> roughly</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Separate the<strong> individual leaves</strong> from the base of the <strong>little gem</strong>, then tear the leaves roughly and add them to your dressing bowl</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>cooked chicken</strong>,<strong> croutons</strong>,&nbsp;half of the<strong>&nbsp;chopped bacon </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/598.-step-7-x400.jpg",
